Syntax: aurabolt <target>

Fires a concentrated bolt of chi/aura energy at an opponent. Aurabolt is a
Pugilist-line unarmed attack skill that channels internal energy into a
single powerful strike. It is handled by the Pugilist attack system (alongside
palmstrike and other unarmed techniques).

Aurabolt is available to Pugilist-class characters and their remort
descendants (Monk, Brawler, and the Martial Artist adept class).

Requirements:
  - Must be in combat or initiates combat on the target.
  - Target must be present in the room.
  - Must have the skill learned.

See also: shelp aurabolt palmstrike punch pummel
